  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マジかよ。
世界樹の闇が
あの化けモンみてェな奴作ったってのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seriously? The World Tree
made that monster-like asshole?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ。
あいつこそまさに世界樹の膿だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. She really is just pure rot of the World Tree.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だったら、あいつを倒せば
世界樹は元の力を取り戻すかもしれない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-In that case, if we beat her, the World Tree
might get its original power back!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まぁありえない話じゃねぇな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, that's sure not impossible.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なら！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やろうぜ、ルカ！
オレ達の力で変えるんだ、世界をよぉ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's get 'er, Ruca!
We'll change the world through our own power!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
